WEBVTT

00:00:28.480 --> 00:00:30.320
Yet we consider it a taboo.

00:00:31.160 --> 00:00:34.040
We feel awkward
and shameful talking about it.

00:00:35.840 --> 00:00:37.656
When I got my first periods,

00:00:37.680 --> 00:00:40.040
I was told to keep it
a secret from others --

00:00:40.760 --> 00:00:42.640
even from my father and brother.

00:00:43.640 --> 00:00:46.256
Later when this chapter
appeared in our textbooks,

00:00:46.280 --> 00:00:48.616
our biology teacher skipped the subject.

00:00:48.640 --> 00:00:51.320
(Laughter)

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:53.680
You know what I learned from it?

00:00:54.360 --> 00:00:57.520
I learned that it is really
shameful to talk about it.

00:00:58.080 --> 00:01:00.736
I learned to be ashamed of my body.